## Inputs and Outputs

| Name | Type | Description | Constraints |
|------|------|-------------|-------------|
| `topic` | `str` | Hierarchical routing key (e.g., `beat.kick`) | Max 255 chars, alphanumeric + dots |
| `payload` | `dict` | Message content | Must be JSON serializable |
| `address` | `str` | ZMQ connection string | e.g. `tcp://127.0.0.1:5555` |

